\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1461268\charrsid1983817 No, my mother was a London}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 
er. My mother was born and bred in London Road. No, it was only my father, he come from Dublin. But - that's - no, that's all their - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Was your mother quite young when she had you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Oh - yes. Well my mother was only twenty 
years older than me - my mother was about twenty when I was born. So my mother was nearly always - twenty years older, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 That's not a lot is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 No, she was only a young woman my mother. No. No, she was good woman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Did she work before she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 
Well she had to - they went to work when they was thirteen, when they was eleven my mother used to have to - what, my old granny had - eighteen children my old granny. And when my mother got married - she had twin sisters laying d
ead, like, you know, they was - been - twin sisters when my mother got married and really - it - if - after my mother - I'd had aunts and uncles - younger than me because they died off. My granny had a - a big family. My grandfather was a blacksmith.

