\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Yes. Oh yes, my - my mother - they always - yes, fourteen, my mother was - a - the - brothers and sisters of fourteen. Had Uncle }{
