\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 You didn't have anyone else living there, no lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Oh no. No, no, no. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Did you ever have anyone to help in the house in your family?
