- pepper and salt that end, pepper and salt this end. And - Sundays used to be a big - jar of - beetroots there and a jar of - 'cos we was big beetroot eaters. With - hot dinners. Yes. Anything - any hot - hot meats. I love beet - I - I can eat a beet - b
eetroot with - like, you know, how used to buy 'em in bundles and eat 'em after I've cooked 'em like an apple. Oh no. No.
