\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 No, no, well we always - my - mother always said, now sit up and eat your dinner properly, or something like that. Oh yes, yes, oh yes.

