ant to hear your troubles, you know, if you've had a - argument you know, you sort it out between yourselves, you know, that -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 If you were worried about something could you go to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Oh yes. Oh good mother that way. Yes, oh yes, she'd help you
 out in every way. Oh yes, oh yes, helped. Oh yes, she never - if you went for any help like you was in trouble or - you know, when after I got married and all that my husband fell on bad times, went up to - ask her you know, well I didn't ask her, I happ
e
ned to meet her and - she said, you don't look very - pleased and that. So she said, where are you going? Oh, I said, down the road and that you know. Well come on, come and have a drink you know and that. So she said, how's the - how's he doing? Out of w
ork. Well here you are, take this and - when he gets - when he gets - on his feet you know where to come, come and see me. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Would you think she was an affectionate person?
