\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Was, it was a lot, yes. Yes. It was, sixpence, yes.
