Oh sweets and - fruit and - and I was a - rare one for raw carrots and turnip, I used to go and buy a ha'penny carrot and ha'penny turnip. I used to eat, 'em, yes. T
ake 'em to school and put 'em under the desk. And I - remember - I remember one day I'm - bending down having a gnaw at a carrot. Teacher said, what are you doing there Rose? I said, nothing. She said, what have you got under there? I said, nothing. She s
aid, well get up and show me. There's a carrot. She said, you had anything to eat? I said, yes. Whatever you eating that for? I said, well I like 'em. Yes. Funny.
