\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Yes. It's funny old I
