Well - well no, well we never - we could never afford - we had to go to school didn't we. No. And my mother couldn't read or write so - we really taught her if we had to - my granny couldn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009338\charrsid1983817 
\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 
 - couldn't read or write but to end - at the end she - really taught herself and as she - used to write and used to write - used to sit down and write and she used to - like - copy it to send to one of my uncle's in the Navy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Well - five I suppose, that was the school age, five, them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 What time did you go in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Well nine o'clock. You was - well the old school bell went at nine and you -
 you used to have to go along and get in by nine. Well after - well, might be after nine you - you know, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 What time did they finish in the afternoons?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Well come out like for dinner was twelve o'clock, went home. Go home for dinner 'til I su
ppose about half past one you went back about quarter to two, the old school bell used to go about quarter to two to go back for the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 What time would you finish then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8213171 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 Four o'clock. 'Course - like when you was in the infants it was four
 o'clock but - when you was in the - higher class it was half past four. Standard six - like - standard - standard six, I think - I don't know if it was seven we went - we finished up. We finished up at half past four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid752558 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10178391\charrsid1983817 What kind of school did you go to?
