 and that and she like fell for a baby, well now - when I see her - next time I see her he'd died, well like and she was left with this little baby. And then - it was the next time, I'm waiting for a bus in - Pall Mall, by old Hamptons that got all bombed
 
down by - Rickham Street. As I'm standing there I looked up, she said, hello. I said, hello. Cor, Gawd, I said, so I said, how are you - how are you getting on? All right. So - I said - she said, how are you getting on Rose? I said, all right. Gilla, not 
